OL,3,CEmpty houses, broken communities: One
OL,4,Cmonth on from the Ballymena riots
OL,6,FA month after riots erupted in
OL,7,FBallymena, ITV News spoke to local
OL,8,Fpeople who denied any suggestion that
OL,9,Fthey were motivated by racism. Report
OL,10,Fby ITV News Correspondent Peter Smith
OL,11,Fand Scotland Producer Stephanie
OL,12,FDocherty
OL,14,FOn Clonavon Terrace in Ballymena,
OL,15,Fempty house after empty house is now
OL,16,Fboarded up.
OL,18,FThis street was at the heart of last
OL,19,Fmonth's week of disorder, which was
OL,20,Faimed mainly against the Roma
OL,21,Fcommunity who had moved into the town.
