OL,3,CEmpty houses, broken communities: One
OL,4,Cmonth on from the Ballymena riots
OL,6,FForeign families were burned out of
OL,7,Ftheir homes, and their landlords were
OL,8,Fwarned not to let them return.
OL,10,FIt started with a protest by the
OL,11,Fcommunity after an alleged sexual
OL,12,Fassault against a local teenage girl.
OL,14,FTwo 14-year-old boys, who spoke in
OL,15,Fcourt through a Romanian interpreter,
OL,16,Fhave since been charged with attempted
OL,17,Frape which they both deny.
