OL,4,Cmonth on from the Ballymena riots
OL,6,FBut the peaceful protest escalated
OL,7,Finto violence, which spread across a
OL,8,Fnumber of towns in Northern Ireland
OL,9,Fover a week of disorder.
OL,11,FHomes were set on fire, windows were
OL,12,Fsmashed, and a number of police
OL,13,Fofficers were injured.
OL,15,FThere have been 41 arrests to date.
OL,17,FOne of those is 18-year-old Michael
OL,18,FElliott.
