OL,6,FHe was arrested in Ballymena on
OL,7,FTuesday, June 10 and charged with
OL,8,Frioting.
OL,10,FHis mum, Carla, agreed to speak to ITV
OL,11,FNews while her son is being held on
OL,12,Fremand.
OL,14,FShe says she is angry that her son's
OL,15,Fface has been used in the press along
OL,16,Fwith the word 'racist'.
OL,18,F"He has been caught up and is being
OL,19,Fused as the scapegoat," she said.
