OL,6,FShe attended what she says was a
OL,7,Fpeaceful protest with Michael and was
OL,8,Fshocked when it turned violent, but
OL,9,Fsays she is not surprised that local
OL,10,Fpeople felt angry over immigration.
OL,12,FShe says she has been warning people
OL,13,Fon her TikTok channel about problems
OL,14,Fin the town for years.
OL,16,F"We've got our own housing crisis. Our
OL,17,Fown people can't get houses. People
OL,18,Fare getting moved in and they get that
OL,19,Fhouse straight away," she said.
OL,21,F"What about our homeless?"
