OL,6,FThe judge remanded Michael into
OL,7,Fcustody, along with others, warning
OL,8,Fthat the violence had caused "great
OL,9,Ffear and trauma" across Northern
OL,10,FIreland.
OL,12,FHe said there needed to be a strong
OL,13,Fmessage that if you are arrested and
OL,14,Fthere is credible and reliable
OL,15,Fevidence, "you will be remanded into
OL,16,Fcustody and ultimately face a lengthy
OL,17,Fcustodial sentence".
OL,19,FDriving around Ballymena now, it is
OL,20,Feasy to see how the town has been
OL,21,Fvisibly changed after the riots.
