OL,6,FMany homes in the town centre have put
OL,7,Fup flags showing symbols of
OL,8,FBritishness or signs highlighting that
OL,9,Flocals live inside to deter any
OL,10,Ffurther damage to their properties.
OL,12,FMilitary veteran Anita has lived here
OL,13,Ffor almost 30 years and is one of
OL,14,Fthose who feels compelled to display a
OL,15,Fflag in every window.
OL,17,F"It says that we are locals, we are
OL,18,FBritish, and don't smash my windows."
