OL,6,F"It (the rioting) was heavy-handed,
OL,7,Fand it was hard, but it did the job.
OL,9,F"They are gone, we've got our streets
OL,10,Fback."
OL,12,FBallymena local councillor, Rodney
OL,13,FQuigley, told ITV News his community
OL,14,Fdoes not have a problem with racism or
OL,15,Fa rise of the far right.
OL,17,FHe says what happened here was about
OL,18,Fone specific group.
OL,20,F"It was the Roma community and I make
OL,21,Fno bones about that.
