OL,6,F"There has been issues with
OL,7,Fprostitution, issues with gangs of
OL,8,Fyoung fellas running around.
OL,10,F"People felt they were being called
OL,11,Fracist because they were concerned
OL,12,Fabout what had been going on."
OL,14,FHe says it was not a race riot, it was
OL,15,Fan anti-Roma riot.
OL,17,F"It doesn't make me a racist calling
OL,18,Fthat out because I would call it out
OL,19,Fin my own community."
