OL,3,CEmpty houses, broken communities: One
OL,4,Cmonth on from the Ballymena riots
OL,6,FThe local primary schools have lost 80
OL,7,Fchildren almost overnight from the
OL,8,Ffamilies that left this area.
OL,10,FOne Romanian family who lives locally
OL,11,Fhad their window smashed in, but told
OL,12,Fus that even though they are still
OL,13,Fbeing intimidated, they are not
OL,14,Fleaving, and this is their home.
OL,16,FAlmost one month on, the streets have
OL,17,Ffallen quiet except for the sound of
OL,18,Frepairs.
