OL,6,FWhat happened here has forced almost
OL,7,Fan entire Roma community to just
OL,8,Fdisappear.
OL,10,FThe violence has stopped, but the
OL,11,Ffeelings of being overlooked and
OL,12,Fignored have not gone away.
